  "text": "The mechanical properties were determined by two mechanical tests: a three-point bending test and an impact test. Because the mechanical properties of the bone differ depending upon the hydration state [CITATION_1] ), special care was taken to keep the specimen fully hydrated right up to the start of the mechanical testing.",
